MINIGAMES

TNTRILLA

bombs explode when you stand on them, And be the last man standing and there is a timer until all the bomb explode and then whoosh, you die.

BEDWARS

You have a bed and if you die you come back to life, if someone breaks your bed and you die, then its game over, use upgrades and get special items to break everyone's bed and kill them, And be the last man standing.

SKYWARS

Whoosh, you just spawned into a island in the sky, you need to get the items of your island chests, build to the middle island, get the better items because ofcourse middle island has better items and then kill everyone And be the last man standing.

VILLAGE DEFENSE

Kill zombies, protect the village, buy better loot from villagers and I will commit suicide.

EARTHITOC SMP

Normal survival with some twists and cool features, also really cool custom terrain!

BLOCK PARTY

So, there are many colourful blocks in the arena, it will tell you to stand on a block with a specific colour and if you don't stand on that block in time you will die, you have to be the last man standing.
